Final Jeopardy
Add setup / information screen
touch version, flip between 2 and 3 player

Keyboard Shortcuts
Escape: Close question or answer popup
U: Unlock Question (optional, default does not lock qustion)
Q: Team 1 answer
P: Team 2 answer
L: Team 3 answer
N: Show Answer
C: Corret Answer
V: Incorrect Answer
M: Close all (same as escape)

Z: FINAL JEOPARDY
S: FINAL JEOPARDY ANSWER!

K: Keyboard shortcut display
I: Show Information
S: Show Settings
H: Show Info Bar / Help Bar

